list.abstract: inspect（英[ɪnˈspekt]，美[ɪnˈspekt]），英语单词，动词，意思为检查；审视；视察。短语搭配有carefully inspect（仔细检查；仔细地检查），例句为“Customs officers came aboard to inspect our documents.（海关官员上船查我们的证件。）” inspect及物动词类近义词有examine、review、visit，名词形式为inspection、inspector、inspectorate。inspected是inspect的过去式和过去分词。

yingyinNormal.en: I want you to bring him in. Let him inspect the paddock. Maybe he sees something we can't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想让你带他过来让他检查下围场的安全度，毕竟旁观者清。
